output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to the given criteria:
1. Has CMF number: Yes - "CMF 11240014" is present at the end of the post, indicating this is electoral propaganda.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes - directly mentions "George Simion" and includes hashtag "#GeorgeSimionPresedinte", who is a presidential candidate.
3. Addresses wide population: Yes - this is a paid Facebook advertisement with significant reach (125,000-150,000 impressions) targeting Timiș region.
4. Electoral objective: Yes - clearly promotes both: - AUR's parliamentary candidates - George Simion for president The message "George Simion are cea mai bună echipă pentru a reconstrui România!" is clearly electoral messaging.
5. Journalism: No - this is clearly promotional content, not journalistic work.
6. Personal opinion: No - this is a structured, paid advertisement with clear electoral messaging and CMF number.
The post violates Article 55 t) as it continues presidential electoral propaganda after the conclusion of the allowed period, while mixing it with parliamentary election messaging.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: - Contains CMF number - Paid advertisement with significant reach - Direct promotion of both parliamentary candidates and presidential candidate - Clear electoral messaging and calls to support - Uses official party channels and messaging
conclusion.message-for-police: UNIWORLD - MEDIA SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin difuzarea unei reclame platite pe Facebook (ID: 3623273844640710) ce continua propaganda electorala pentru candidatul prezidential George Simion dupa incheierea perioadei legale de campanie. Postarea, activa dupa ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, promoveaza explicit candidatura prezidentiala prin utilizarea hashtag-ului "#GeorgeSimionPresedinte" si mesaje de sustinere directa, fiind o reclama platita cu impact semnificativ (125,000-150,000 afisari). Materialul include cod CMF 11240014, confirmand natura sa de propaganda electorala.
